msgctxt "128_Akiyama"
msgid "Hey, how'd your little session with Sugiuchi go?"
msgstr "Hey, qué tal."

msgctxt "140_Kido"
msgid "Ugh, don't get me started."
msgstr "Buenas."

msgctxt "152_Kido"
msgid "That guy really puts the dick in detective. What an asshole."
msgstr "Ahh, ese tal Sugiuchi, el detective... de verdad tiene una personalidad de mierda, ¿no?"

msgctxt "164_Akiyama"
msgid "No joke."
msgstr "Sí... Bueno, tiene más de cuarenta y sigue estancado en ese puesto, ¿no?"

msgctxt "176_Akiyama"
msgid "But hey, if I were over forty and still stuck as a beat cop, I'd probably have a chip on my shoulder, too."
msgstr "Debe estar frustrado... Seguro que sí."

msgctxt "188_Kido"
msgid "You think that's all it is?"
msgstr "¿Tú crees que es solo eso?"

msgctxt "200_Akiyama"
msgid "You think it's not?"
msgstr "¿A qué te refieres?"

msgctxt "272_Kido"
msgid "I dunno. It kinda feels like he's, like, obsessed with you and Arai-aniki or something."
msgstr "Es que ese tal Sugiuchi... solo me hacía preguntas sobre usted y Arai-aniki."

msgctxt "284_Akiyama"
msgid "How do you figure?"
msgstr "¿Sobre Arai y yo?"

msgctxt "296_Kido"
msgid "He kept grilling me about how you two met."
msgstr "Sí. Que cómo se conocieron ustedes dos, por ejemplo."

msgctxt "308_Kido"
msgid "Oh, and he wouldn't shut up about wanting to know what Kanemura's loan terms were."
msgstr "Que cuáles fueron las condiciones para que usted le prestara dinero a nuestro jefe..."

msgctxt "320_Kido"
msgid "Doesn't that seem kinda... weird to you?"
msgstr "¿No le parece raro?"

msgctxt "332_Akiyama"
msgid "I guess."
msgstr "Sí, un poco."

msgctxt "344_Kido"
msgid "Not that I can blame him for wondering. Why <Italic>are</Italic> you throwing your weight behind Arai-aniki?"
msgstr "Pero igual, yo también tengo curiosidad. ¿Por qué se involucra tanto usted por Arai-aniki?"

msgctxt "356_Akiyama"
msgid "That's my little secret."
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "368_Kido"
msgid "C'mon, Akiyama-san! You can tell me."
msgstr "Akiyama-san. Dígamelo, por favor."

msgctxt "380_Akiyama"
msgid "Heh, maybe when you're older."
msgstr "Será en otra ocasión."

msgctxt "392_Kido"
msgid "Ugh, Akiyama-san..."
msgstr "Akiyama-san..."

